Qin'er.

280
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:52,510
This one.

281
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:53,740
How about this one?

282
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:55,840
Fa'ke, you have fair skin and a rosy face.

283
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,370
You already look stunning.

284
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:58,880
Really?

285
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,740
Then I'll go like this.

286
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:01,790
Just go.

287
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:03,170
Mr. Lu must be getting anxious.

288
00:15:03,170 --> 00:15:03,870
Go.

289
00:15:12,050 --> 00:15:13,910
If you like it, please come often.

290
00:15:14,610 --> 00:15:16,250
Lu. Lu.

291
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,390
Pan'er.

292
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,210
Lu. Lu.

293
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:23,640
All you ever think about is your Lu.

294
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:25,840
Why not sit down and have some tea first?

295
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:28,140
Pan'er, stop teasing me.

296
00:15:28,410 --> 00:15:29,600
Is Lu here?

297
00:15:29,710 --> 00:15:30,240
I'm here.

298
00:15:45,650 --> 00:15:47,030
♪ When it comes to spacing out ♪

299
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:48,410
♪ I'm the best in the world ♪

300
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,010
♪ Sometimes I throw a little tantrum ♪

301
00:15:50,570 --> 00:15:52,120
♪ But my mind is full of you ♪

302
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:53,840
♪ Even if you leave my thoughts in ruins ♪

303
00:15:54,450 --> 00:15:55,320
♪ I won't really mind ♪

304
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:57,250
♪ Stumbling along while singing out loud ♪

305
00:15:57,900 --> 00:15:58,650
♪ Di da da da di ♪

306
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,640
♪ When it comes to acting cute ♪

307
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:02,150
♪ I'm the best in the world ♪

308
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:02,840
Do you like it?

309
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:03,650
♪ Every day will be sweet ♪

310
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:04,990
I like everything you choose.

311
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,910
♪ This is my game ♪

312
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,520
♪ From now on ♪

313
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:09,030
♪ I'll be your mystery ♪

314
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:10,920
♪ Gentle, cute, spoiled, proud ♪

315
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,500
♪ Di da da da di ♪

316
00:16:22,710 --> 00:16:25,470
I didn't expect Mr. Shi
to fall for such a trick.

317
00:16:31,260 --> 00:16:33,050
Let's go then.

318
00:16:45,930 --> 00:16:46,670
Go where?

319
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:47,980
It's already noon.

320
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,920
Time for lunch, of course.

321
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:50,610
Come on.

322
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:52,440
We'll first buy some plum syrup.

323
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,260
And then,

324
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,360
we'll pick up the roast chicken
I ordered yesterday.

325
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,910
Across from the roast chicken shop,
there's a rice noodle place.

326
00:16:57,910 --> 00:17:00,210
We'll eat and rest there a bit.

327
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:01,570
After lunch,

328
00:17:01,590 --> 00:17:03,550
I'll take you to the Peony Garden
to enjoy flowers.

329
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:06,069
Then we'll go to the opera house
for a play.

330
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:08,170
If you're hungry after the play,

331
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:09,920
we can go eat some mini wontons.

332
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:20,800
Chongshan.

333
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:22,849
I'm late.

334
00:17:22,869 --> 00:17:24,390
Not at all.

335
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,280
Let's take a walk around then.

336
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:55,760
[Shoe Shop]

337
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,480
It's quite cute.

338
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,180
What's this?

339
00:17:53,180 --> 00:17:53,870
Take a look.

340
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:54,810
It's a puppy.

341
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:56,840
What do you think?

342
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,040
It's okay.

343
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:01,280
Let's go look at something else.

344
00:18:01,510 --> 00:18:02,000
Okay.

345
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:06,770
Lu Yi.

346
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:09,480
Miss Qin'er.

347
00:18:15,110 --> 00:18:17,200
Miss Qin'er, have you ever ridden a horse?

348
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:19,770
No. I'm a bit scared.

349
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:20,600
Don't be afraid.

350
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,740
Come on, I'll ride with you.

351
00:18:21,740 --> 00:18:22,870
It's very obedient.

352
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:25,320
Be careful.

353
00:18:27,730 --> 00:18:28,460
Is this okay?

354
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:39,760
Go back.

355
00:18:40,910 --> 00:18:42,510
Why have we arrived so soon?

356
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,290
It's not like
we won't see each other again.

357
00:18:44,290 --> 00:18:46,890
I'll pick you up
first thing tomorrow morning.

358
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:47,790
Oh no!

359
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:49,740
My brothers are back!

360
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:50,660
Hurry!

361
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:06,110
-Where did you go?
-Where did you go?

362
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:10,400
-What's that in your hand?
-What's that in your hand?

363
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,530
I am your elder brother.

364
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:14,310
How dare you speak to me like that?

365
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,190
Xianxian, same to you.

366
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:17,350
You'd better behave.

367
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,910
After they go inside,

368
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:19,790
you sneak out.

369
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:21,730
Your two brothers know me.

370
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:23,350
Why should I act stealthily?

371
00:19:23,540 --> 00:19:24,880
I might as well go say hello to them.

372
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,750
No, don't go out there.

373
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:27,280
Mind your own business.

374
00:19:27,280 --> 00:19:28,750
-Mind your own business too.
-Give me a kiss,

375
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:29,750
and I won't go out.

376
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,180
Xianxian, Chongshan.

377
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:55,960
Where did you go?

378
00:19:55,990 --> 00:19:57,190
-Nowhere.
-Nowhere.

379
00:19:57,630 --> 00:19:58,030
Go.

380
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:04,480
[Yachun House]

381
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,610
Nothing?

382
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:03,510
Wait.

383
00:20:08,630 --> 00:20:10,690
So they're hiding something from me.

384
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,970
Oh.

385
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:14,260
-Oh?
-Oh?

386
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,040
Wait,

387
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,510
what does that mean, Ke?

388
00:20:17,290 --> 00:20:21,910
[Yachun House]

389
00:20:18,540 --> 00:20:19,980
What do you know?

390
00:20:20,610 --> 00:20:21,590
Ke, don't go!

391
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:22,070
Ke!

392
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:34,840
Ketian.

393
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:43,370
Kexian, why are you still up at this hour?

394
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,030
When have you ever come home this late?

395
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,280
I was worried when you were not home.

396
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:50,510
I couldn't sleep.

397
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:54,260
You're the best, Kexian.

398
00:20:54,490 --> 00:20:56,220
I want to stay with you forever.

399
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,760
What are you talking about?

400
00:20:58,760 --> 00:21:00,330
You'll get married someday.

401
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:01,810
Chongshan will treat you well.

402
00:21:01,810 --> 00:21:04,370
Kexian, I don't want to get married.

403
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:06,210
I want to stay with you forever.

404
00:21:06,900 --> 00:21:08,960
Kexian, when will you get married?

405
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:11,340
When will you marry that annoying Ke?

406
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:15,910
Ke...

407
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:18,360
I also want to marry Ke soon.

408
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,650
But...

409
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:24,600
If you marry Ke,

410
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,280
we can all live together.

411
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:29,700
Then we can play together every day.

412
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:32,490
Even if Ke moves in,

413
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:35,260
you'll have to move into the Shi family.

414
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:40,250
Kexian, what nonsense
are you talking about?

415
00:21:40,670 --> 00:21:42,820
It's late. I'm going to bed.

416
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:44,370
You should sleep early too.

417
00:21:44,820 --> 00:21:45,760
I'm leaving.

418
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:47,440
May your wishes come true too.

419
00:21:53,190 --> 00:21:55,430
[Yachun House]

420
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,310
This is strange.

421
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:58,230
It's fine that Xianxian
ate roast chicken alone,

422
00:21:58,230 --> 00:22:00,160
but he also went to have plum syrup.

423
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:02,640
He must've gone to meet some young lady.

424
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:05,350
Pan'er left early.

425
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,580
Could it be they...

426
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:11,290
Nothing escapes me.

427
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:14,070
Chongshan was acting strange too.

428
00:22:14,570 --> 00:22:16,930
Why did he smell like pastries

429
00:22:17,180 --> 00:22:18,780
but come home empty-handed?

430
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:20,590
Did he go to He's Bakery?

431
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:22,610
Whatever.

432
00:22:22,950 --> 00:22:25,480
Sooner or later,
I'll catch them red-handed.

433
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:37,840
Lu, why are you here?

434
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:40,270
Your kiss was too sweet.
How could I sleep?

435
00:22:40,850 --> 00:22:42,220
Such a smooth talker.

436
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,830
Just in time.
I have something to tell you.

437
00:22:45,980 --> 00:22:47,970
I'm going to be busy these days.

438
00:22:48,430 --> 00:22:49,120
Why?

439
00:22:49,410 --> 00:22:51,630
It's time to prepare
for your brother's wedding.

440
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:53,900
And my two brothers seem to have
their own situations too.

441
00:22:53,900 --> 00:22:55,430
I know about Zhuxi's marriage.

442
00:22:55,430 --> 00:22:56,950
But what's going on
with your two brothers?

443
00:22:56,950 --> 00:22:59,360
Both of them went on dates today.

444
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:02,740
Looks like I need to work harder then.

445
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:04,040
Or I'll fall behind.

446
00:23:05,370 --> 00:23:06,250
Nonsense.

447
00:23:07,460 --> 00:23:09,450
Fa'ke, have you gone to bed?

448
00:23:09,470 --> 00:23:10,330
Qin'er is here.

449
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:12,160
Lu, you should leave now.

450
00:23:13,090 --> 00:23:14,320
Stop joking.

451
00:23:14,340 --> 00:23:15,850
If I kiss you again,
you won't be able to sleep.

452
00:23:15,850 --> 00:23:16,450
I can sleep just fine.

453
00:23:16,450 --> 00:23:16,920
Go.

454
00:23:17,090 --> 00:23:18,110
Go now.

455
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,220
I'm closing the window.

456
00:23:19,220 --> 00:23:20,370
Go. Hurry.

457
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:25,310
Fa'ke, I can't sleep.

458
00:23:25,330 --> 00:23:27,170
I want to sleep with you tonight.

459
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,830
Sure.

460
00:23:30,290 --> 00:23:33,090
But why is your face so red?

461
00:23:33,630 --> 00:23:35,890
Maybe it's too hot tonight.

462
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,020
Let's open the window for some fresh air.

463
00:23:37,020 --> 00:23:37,500
No, no!

464
00:23:39,270 --> 00:23:41,230
The wind is strong at night.

465
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:42,550
We might catch a cold.

466
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,430
Let's go to bed now.

467
00:23:52,850 --> 00:23:55,320
Miss Shi, did you sleep well last night?

468
00:23:56,020 --> 00:23:57,030
Well enough.

469
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,400
Just you must avoid sweets before bed,

470
00:23:59,410 --> 00:24:01,140
or you might suffer from insomnia.

471
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:02,900
I'll remember your wise advice.

472
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:04,430
I want to ask you for a favor.

473
00:24:04,570 --> 00:24:06,960
My younger brother Lu Zhuxi is in love
with someone.

474
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:10,030
Would you be willing to be his matchmaker?

475
00:24:10,590 --> 00:24:13,380
I'm happy to help.

476
00:24:20,190 --> 00:24:21,260
Ke.

477
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:23,120
You know Miss Zhu best.

478
00:24:24,210 --> 00:24:26,510
How many betrothal gifts
should I prepare for Zhuxi?

479
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:28,440
Yanyan doesn't care about wealth.

480
00:24:28,930 --> 00:24:30,130
What matters most is

481
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,770
that their hearts are aligned.

482
00:24:31,770 --> 00:24:33,220
If their hearts truly speak as one,

483
00:24:33,220 --> 00:24:35,160
and Mr. Lu shows his sincerity,

484
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,740
he'll win Yanyan's heart.

485
00:24:37,570 --> 00:24:40,700
But the Zhu family is
the Prime Minister's household,

486
00:24:40,970 --> 00:24:42,310
with high status and power.

487
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:44,770
So proper etiquette
must still be observed.

488
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,490
Lu.

489
00:24:48,040 --> 00:24:50,000
This is a gift list I prepared.

490
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,650
Just prepare according to this.

491
00:24:51,650 --> 00:24:52,380
Ms. Li.

492
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:57,730
Chief, what can I do for you?

493
00:24:57,750 --> 00:24:59,890
This is the list
of betrothal gifts for Miss Zhu.

494
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:01,890
Prepare everything according to this list.

495
00:25:01,890 --> 00:25:02,440
Yes.

496
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,920
Pan'er, please wait.

497
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:09,340
What do you think
of these betrothal gifts?

498
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:12,290
I don't know much about Miss Zhu,

499
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,880
so I don't really have an opinion.

500
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,100
I meant

501
00:25:15,330 --> 00:25:17,630
what you think of betrothal gifts

502
00:25:17,790 --> 00:25:18,590
for yourself.

503
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:24,390
I don't know. Don't ask me.

504
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,900
I have no thoughts on that.

505
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:27,640
If you don't know,

506
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:30,340
I'll ask Xianxian.

507
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:37,960
Seems like my guess is right.

508
00:25:40,330 --> 00:25:40,860
Brother.

509
00:25:41,990 --> 00:25:43,450
Miss Shi, you're here too.

510
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,090
Forgive me.

511
00:25:48,210 --> 00:25:50,500
I should call you Sister-in-law.

512
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:56,570
Lu,
your younger brother is smooth-tongued.

513
00:25:57,440 --> 00:26:00,210
Looks like I need to work harder.

514
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:02,360
I just saw Ms. Li

515
00:26:02,430 --> 00:26:04,760
leaving with a list, her face all flushed.

516
00:26:04,900 --> 00:26:07,430
Were you two discussing
something important?

517
00:26:07,430 --> 00:26:08,800
It was for you.

518
00:26:09,060 --> 00:26:09,880
For me?

519
00:26:10,150 --> 00:26:11,380
That's a list

520
00:26:11,690 --> 00:26:14,420
of betrothal gifts
for my future sister-in-law.

521
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:17,310
Really?

522
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:19,640
Brother, Sister-in-law,
you're so nice to me.

523
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,480
Mr. Lu.

524
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:23,070
I know you and Yanyan love each other.

525
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:25,200
But the Prime Minister's household is
different from ordinary ones.

526
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:27,550
The etiquette must be observed properly,
and betrothal gifts must be complete.

527
00:26:27,550 --> 00:26:29,530
I know. Don't worry, Sister-in-law.

528
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:31,530
Sister-in-law, just call me Zhuxi.

529
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:32,910
Zhuxi,

530
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:35,310
I know what kind of person Yanyan is.

531
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:37,040
She doesn't care about money or status.

532
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:38,240
All she wants

533
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:40,190
is someone who understands her

534
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,850
and stays by her side forever.

535
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,940
So Zhuxi, can you promise me

536
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:46,590
that for the rest of your life,

537
00:26:46,590 --> 00:26:48,050
you'll treat Yanyan well?

538
00:26:48,300 --> 00:26:48,830
I can.

539
00:26:49,490 --> 00:26:50,690
Not just in this life,

540
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:52,380
in the next life and the one after that,

541
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:54,240
I will always be with her.

542
00:26:54,470 --> 00:26:56,910
Also, Yanyan loves reading novels,

543
00:26:57,130 --> 00:26:58,810
especially Neighboring Hermit's novels.

544
00:26:58,810 --> 00:27:00,610
Write more for her in the future.

545
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,650
Sister-in-law,

546
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:03,440
that won't be a problem.

547
00:27:03,950 --> 00:27:05,860
Even if she wants me to write every day,

548
00:27:05,860 --> 00:27:07,090
I would do so willingly.

549
00:27:07,090 --> 00:27:07,830
That's good.

550
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,350
Once the betrothal gifts are ready,

551
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,880
we'll go propose marriage.

552
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:14,240
Thank you, Brother, Sister-in-law.

553
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,970
I won't disturb you anymore.

554
00:27:16,450 --> 00:27:17,180
I'm leaving.

555
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:17,880
Go.

556
00:27:40,690 --> 00:27:43,030
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

557
00:27:53,570 --> 00:27:55,750
Why... why are you here

558
00:27:55,770 --> 00:27:57,190
in broad daylight?

559
00:27:57,210 --> 00:27:59,440
I came because I wanted to see you.

560
00:28:00,940 --> 00:28:04,740
But during the day, there are people
coming and going in the mansion.

561
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:07,080
You've seen me. Leave quickly.

562
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,090
I'm not leaving.

563
00:28:13,810 --> 00:28:17,180
You spend every day
with Neighboring Hermit's novels,

564
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:20,070
while I can hardly see you.

565
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:22,800
I think you like him more.

566
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,820
Don't talk nonsense.

567
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,240
My brother

568
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:28,440
is helping me prepare betrothal gifts.

569
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:31,040
Miss Shi will come
to propose on my behalf soon.

570
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,500
By then,

571
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:35,670
I can stay with you day and night.

572
00:28:37,350 --> 00:28:38,510
Okay. I see.

573
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:43,650
Yanyan.

574
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,610
We're about to get married.

575
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:48,020
Before our wedding,

576
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:51,090
I want to confess something to you.

577
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,800
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

578
00:29:00,110 --> 00:29:01,070
Could it be

579
00:29:01,770 --> 00:29:04,190
you also have a little girl in your heart,

580
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:06,670
just like the story in the novel?

581
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,940
Actually, I...

582
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,660
Actually,

583
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:13,370
there's someone
who has always cared about me.

584
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:19,540
Yanyan!

585
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:22,170
Then why are you still...

586
00:29:22,790 --> 00:29:24,450
still pestering me like this?

587
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:26,020
Lu Zhuxi,

588
00:29:26,050 --> 00:29:28,400
I only want someone
who loves me wholeheartedly.

589
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:31,080
Don't come to me anymore!

590
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:33,440
Yanyan, I was just joking.

591
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:35,770
No, it wasn't really a joke.

592
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:36,390
You...

593
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,500
Yanyan, look at this.

594
00:29:42,130 --> 00:29:43,020
I don't want to.

595
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:48,350
Yanyan, look at this seal.

596
00:29:51,670 --> 00:29:53,370
[Seal of Neighboring Hermit]

597
00:29:54,970 --> 00:29:55,770
Isn't this...

598
00:29:56,680 --> 00:29:59,360
isn't this the seal of Neighboring Hermit?

599
00:29:59,690 --> 00:30:00,620
Why do you...

600
00:30:02,470 --> 00:30:05,490
Could it be you are Neighboring Hermit?

601
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:10,690
I said someone's secretly cared about me.

602
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:12,370
I wasn't lying, right?

603
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:15,940
How... how could you do this?

604
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:18,530
You knew I admire Neighboring Hermit.

605
00:30:18,550 --> 00:30:21,120
You knew and you still teased me.

606
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:22,460
I was just joking.

607
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:34,710
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

608
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,140
Greetings, Lord Zhu.

609
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:37,730
This is Lu Zhuxi,
the second young master of Xibao Pavilion.

610
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:40,760
He's brought betrothal gifts
to propose to Miss Zhu.

611
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,830
Greetings, Lord Zhu.

612
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:44,940
I am Lu Zhuxi.

613
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,510
My pen name is Neighboring Hermit.

614
00:30:46,510 --> 00:30:48,270
My family has modest wealth,
free of financial worry.

615
00:30:48,270 --> 00:30:50,220
Miss Zhu and I share common interests

616
00:30:50,220 --> 00:30:51,430
and deep affection.

617
00:30:51,610 --> 00:30:53,620
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

618
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,710
I sincerely wish to marry Miss Zhu.

619
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:56,440
After marriage, we will cherish
and understand each other.

620
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,700
Please approve.

621
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:09,890
Lord Zhu,

622
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:12,120
since my mother
became an official matchmaker,

623
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:13,870
you have always been an honored guest
in our family.

624
00:31:13,870 --> 00:31:15,800
And Yanyan and I are close friends.

625
00:31:15,930 --> 00:31:17,330
I've always wanted to find Yanyan

626
00:31:17,330 --> 00:31:20,710
someone who understands her, loves her,
and cherishes her.

627
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:23,940
Now I've truly found such a person.

628
00:31:24,170 --> 00:31:26,370
I'm willing to be Yanyan's matchmaker.

629
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:30,390
Miss Shi, no need to say more.

630
00:31:30,810 --> 00:31:33,690
Our families are indeed close.

631
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:37,010
You and your mother are both
great marriage brokers.

632
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,160
But

633
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:41,910
I'd like to ask Mr. Lu a few questions.

634
00:31:41,930 --> 00:31:42,930
Please, Lord Zhu.

635
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:46,270
The Zhu family has served
as officials for generations,

636
00:31:46,270 --> 00:31:47,750
with four generations
as the Prime Minister.

637
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:50,830
Although Xibao Pavilion has great wealth,

638
00:31:51,570 --> 00:31:53,450
I've never cared a bit.

639
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:57,730
The Zhu family lacks
neither money nor power.

640
00:31:58,130 --> 00:31:59,650
There is nothing in this world

641
00:31:59,650 --> 00:32:03,000
more precious than my Yanyan.

642
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:06,280
Mr. Lu, you want to marry

643
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:08,650
the only young lady
of Prime Minister's Mansion

644
00:32:08,650 --> 00:32:11,950
with just a few well-written books
and sweet words?

645
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,960
Lord Zhu, I...

646
00:32:17,570 --> 00:32:18,430
Lord Zhu,

647
00:32:19,130 --> 00:32:21,260
Yanyan lost her parents at a young age.

648
00:32:21,290 --> 00:32:23,620
Her stepmother has never cared about her.

649
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:25,060
You love her,

650
00:32:25,080 --> 00:32:27,410
so you kept her by your side
and raised her.

651
00:32:27,730 --> 00:32:30,850
I know Yanyan is the apple of your eye.

652
00:32:31,070 --> 00:32:32,800
She gets everything she wants.

653
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:34,250
You love her so much,

654
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,150
so you wouldn't care whether her suitor

655
00:32:36,150 --> 00:32:38,930
has money, an official rank, or power.

656
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:41,240
What you truly care about

657
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:43,380
is whether Yanyan can be happy

658
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:44,610
and safe.

659
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,750
I believe

660
00:32:48,970 --> 00:32:51,460
Mr. Lu understands this deeply.

661
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:00,200
Lord Zhu, please rest assured.

662
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:01,720
I will never let Yanyan suffer.

663
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:03,780
I will stay by Yanyan's side every day

664
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:05,560
and care about her in every way.

665
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:16,110
Let's discuss this matter another day.

666
00:33:16,530 --> 00:33:17,940
You two may leave now.

667
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,180
Steward, see them out.

668
00:33:24,490 --> 00:33:26,670
Honored guests, please leave.

669
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:32,180
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

670
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:36,340
[Graceful Dwelling in Spring's Glow]

671
00:33:38,540 --> 00:33:40,330
Grandfather wouldn't approve.

672
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:42,120
What should I do?

673
