How did things go?

674
00:34:02,550 --> 00:34:05,450
Zhuxi, don't be discouraged.

675
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:06,910
You should know

676
00:34:06,930 --> 00:34:09,889
Lord Zhu cherishes and loves
his granddaughter above all else.

677
00:34:09,889 --> 00:34:11,199
So he should think carefully

678
00:34:11,199 --> 00:34:12,570
when it comes
to choosing a husband for her.

679
00:34:12,570 --> 00:34:14,790
It's normal
we don't succeed in just one attempt.

680
00:34:14,790 --> 00:34:18,690
Besides, he didn't refuse you either.

681
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,909
Don't be discouraged.

682
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:28,590
Yanyan endured hardship in her childhood,

683
00:34:28,590 --> 00:34:30,550
yet she remains optimistic and cheerful.

684
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,750
