685
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,610
I must treat her better.

686
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:39,100
I'll marry no one but Yanyan in this life.

687
00:34:43,199 --> 00:34:44,310
Since you said that,

688
00:34:44,310 --> 00:34:45,710
as your marriage broker,

689
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:47,620
I'll see this through to the end.

690
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:49,280
Think about all the matches I made before.

691
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:51,010
None of them succeeded on the first try.

692
00:34:51,010 --> 00:34:51,840
Rest assured.

693
00:34:52,179 --> 00:34:54,500
I'll make sure you marry her.

694
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:01,820
Yanyan.

695
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,350
I see.

696
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:10,590
I refused that man
from Xibao Pavilion today.

697
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:12,650
So you're angry, right?

698
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:16,590
Yanyan, you can tell me

699
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:18,010
what you think.

700
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:21,290
Grandfather.

701
00:35:22,520 --> 00:35:25,120
I do have feelings for Mr. Lu.

702
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:27,590
He is well-educated
but wouldn't take the imperial exams.

703
00:35:27,590 --> 00:35:30,080
Even with his family's vast wealth,

704
00:35:30,290 --> 00:35:31,930
he's still just a merchant.

705
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:34,460
A match like this isn't considered proper.

706
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:36,460
Have you thought about what it means

707
00:35:36,590 --> 00:35:38,120
to marry into such a family?

708
00:35:38,470 --> 00:35:39,440
Grandfather,

709
00:35:39,460 --> 00:35:42,630
