one can be worry-free for life.

710
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,620
Besides,

711
00:35:43,650 --> 00:35:46,240
I want to marry someone I truly love.

712
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:49,800
I don't care about his status,
family background, or official rank.

713
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:52,300
I agree with you.

714
00:35:52,660 --> 00:35:54,660
I'll judge him solely by character.

715
00:35:55,090 --> 00:35:59,340
He's sweet-tongued now,

716
00:36:00,180 --> 00:36:01,640
but what about the future?

717
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:04,080
How long can his affection last?

718
00:36:04,150 --> 00:36:05,380
Grandfather.

719
00:36:06,210 --> 00:36:08,560
Grandfather. Do you remember

720
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:11,160
I was in danger at the Flower Assembly?

721
00:36:11,370 --> 00:36:14,210
He rescued me from the fire

722
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,650
without any hesitation.

723
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:18,090
In that moment of peril, he was decisive.

724
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,940
I believe he is a reliable person.

725
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:23,100
Such a deed

726
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:25,000
may prove his character,

727
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:27,830
but it's not enough to prove his nature.

728
00:36:28,610 --> 00:36:31,720
A real man should show persistence

729
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:34,230
and unwavering courage.

730
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,800
Grandfather.

731
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,840
If his feelings for you are sincere,

732
00:36:38,590 --> 00:36:40,620
he should prove it to me,

733
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,940
instead of letting you

734
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,540
plead with me.

735
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:46,530
How about this?

736
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,680
If he can pass my test,

737
00:36:48,850 --> 00:36:50,560
we'll discuss the rest later.

738
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:52,990
Grandfather,

739
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:53,920
I believe he

740
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:56,060
can surely pass your test.

741
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:02,070
[Zhu's Mansion]

742
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,610
Mr. Lu.

743
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:09,290
Mr. Lu.

744
00:37:11,510 --> 00:37:13,390
Yanyan, I'm here.

745
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:24,440
Yanyan.

746
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,500
Mr. Lu, you finally came.

747
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:29,750
So you were waiting for me.

748
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:35,000
I brought you this.

749
00:37:35,710 --> 00:37:37,330
I wrote new chapters

750
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,530
and specially brought them to you.

751
00:37:38,530 --> 00:37:41,260
I was worried
you might be tired of the old novels.

752
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,180
Thank you.

753
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:46,900
I never imagined my long-cherished wish
would finally come true.

754
