Yanyan, I...

755
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:51,610
I want to ask...

756
00:37:53,290 --> 00:37:56,390
You want to ask about my feelings for you?

757
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:59,230
I told Miss Shi and my brother today

758
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,670
that I'll marry no one but you.

759
00:38:00,670 --> 00:38:02,400
My feelings will never change.

760
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:09,080
Do you know how I feel about you?

761
00:38:16,640 --> 00:38:19,690
I, Zhu Yanyan, in this life,

762
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,290
will marry only Lu Zhuxi.

763
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,280
This resolve will never change.

