00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,900
But I heard from Chongshan

832
00:41:43,930 --> 00:41:45,600
that Ke has been going
to Xibao Pavilion a lot.

833
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:47,840
And she wants to help arrange a marriage
for Lu Chi's younger brother.

834
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,420
Kexian,

835
00:41:48,550 --> 00:41:49,550
you can't let Lu Chi

836
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,610
get the upper hand at a time like this.

837
00:41:58,940 --> 00:42:00,000
If that's the case,

838
00:42:02,380 --> 00:42:04,170
it's Ke's own choice.

839
00:42:10,310 --> 00:42:11,520
[Shi's Mansion]

840
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,930
Lu, thank you.

841
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:19,550
You should go back and rest early.

842
00:42:19,550 --> 00:42:20,140
You too.

843
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,380
Ke!

844
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:24,430
Come here!

845
00:42:24,470 --> 00:42:25,220
You go there!

846
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,040
You...

847
00:42:28,150 --> 00:42:29,280
Xianxian, Chongshan,

848
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,420
tell me

849
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:31,790
where you went first.

850
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,470
-I...
-I...

851
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:39,020
Xianxian.

852
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:42,460
The moon is so beautiful tonight, right?

853
00:42:42,880 --> 00:42:45,340
Yes, look how big the moon is!

854
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:50,290
Go.

855
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:54,520
Xianxian, Chongshan, I'm leaving.

856
00:42:55,510 --> 00:42:56,330
Lu Chi!

857
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:57,250
You...

858
00:42:57,350 --> 00:42:58,810
Don't let me see you again.

859
00:42:59,140 --> 00:42:59,710
Ke!

860
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:00,230
Ke!

861
00:43:00,230 --> 00:43:01,160
I'm going to bed!

862
00:43:03,210 --> 00:43:03,970
Oh, no.

863
00:43:04,270 --> 00:43:05,920
Father told us to keep an eye on Ke.

864
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:07,570
It seems she went on a date
with Lu Chi again.

865
00:43:07,570 --> 00:43:09,470
Not "seems." She did.

866
00:43:09,890 --> 00:43:10,690
Don't worry, Xianxian.

867
00:43:10,690 --> 00:43:11,620
We still have Father.

868
00:43:11,620 --> 00:43:13,970
That's right, we still have Father.

869
00:43:14,470 --> 00:43:15,870
So it's not a big problem.

870
00:44:08,360 --> 00:44:09,000
You...

871
00:44:24,650 --> 00:44:25,480
Lu.

872
00:44:29,670 --> 00:44:31,190
Ke, you're here.

873
00:44:33,320 --> 00:44:34,140
Lu.

874
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,140
Do you think

875
00:44:36,360 --> 00:44:37,400
if we don't see each other for days,

876
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:38,460
when we meet again,

877
00:44:38,630 --> 00:44:40,090
we'd be happier than before?

878
00:44:40,090 --> 00:44:41,550
Why should we not see each other for days?

